Package: GenomicDataStream
Type: Package
Title: Read genomic data files (VCF, BCF, BGEN, PGEN, BED, H5AD) into
        R/Rcpp in chunks
Version: 0.0.13
Date: 2025-01-29
Authors@R: person("Gabriel", "Hoffman", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="gabriel.hoffman@mssm.edu", comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-0957-0224"))
Description: Read genomic data files (i.e. VCF, BCF, BGEN, PGEN, BED, H5AD, DelayedArray) into R/Rcpp in chunks for analysis with Armadillo or Eigen libraries.  
